{"tid":2212761,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"就是不公平，你吹呀？ - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-09-22T04:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T07:26:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0b1a3b24019eb6bad14693c24e9e38024c72fcf7","tid":2212761,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:58:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200922/B4SVKPQUFJHY3OOJ3CI6NU74EY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200922%2FB4SVKPQUFJHY3OOJ3CI6NU74EY%2F&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEQ2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=af6eba15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200922%2FB4SVKPQUFJHY3OOJ3CI6NU74EY%2F&h=482a3154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200922/B4SVKPQUFJHY3OOJ3CI6NU74EY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n就是不公平，你吹呀？ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Uq3_cdjBE0I1icM80CUnuUr8V_Y=/1656x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S7XD3PQ7LFARLHEIJNB3PLHL3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUq3_cdjBE0I1icM80CUnuUr8V_Y%3D%2F1656x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS7XD3PQ7LFARLHEIJNB3PLHL3Q.jpg&h=8911f9ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n84歲老翁黃森球於中聯辦大樓一帶向「長毛」梁國雄施襲，以金屬製的尖鑿刺傷梁的右腰，被控襲擊致造成身體傷害罪。案件近日提堂，裁判官以疑犯「熱愛社會」為由，准許他繼續保釋。疑犯更公開宣告，一個許智峯，一個黃之鋒，兩個遲早都要死。疑犯涉嫌恐嚇，亦無受到法律懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n與上述案件非常相似的一個案例，是男子董栢輝，以小刀割傷何君堯乳頭。董被控以企圖謀殺及傷人等重罪，被捕近一年，一直被押，無法保釋。<br />\n<br />\n若因政見不同，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n今日香港，三權分立被否定，司法不公成為日常，律政司肆意介入大小官司，選擇加控或撤控。性質相同的案件，可以有不同的判法。人治取代了法治。<br />\n<br />\n同一個法官，對已經實施犯罪行為，刺傷長毛的疑犯，盛讚其「熱愛社會」，批准保釋。對被搜出48條索帶，但並未用索帶做任何事，既無犯罪意圖、更無犯罪行為者，卻重判5個半月且拒絕保釋。這就是面目全非的今日香港。危牆之下無完卵，每個香港人，都可以是攜帶索帶被送入黑獄的人。你不服嗎？就是不公平，你吹呀？"},{"pid":"fa9b39a5b57f27162d85b69487c6a548ce4f3f3a","tid":2212761,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:26:10.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}